README
===================

GIMP Beautify is a set of GIMP plug-ins for quick and easy beautify photo.

INSTALL
===================

method 1 - install into mathine directory:

make
sudo make install

method 2 - install into user directory:
make
make userinstall

Note:
Be sure that you have installed the gimp-devel-tools package before install.

USING
===================

GIMP menu:
Tools -> Beautify -> Beautify
Tools -> Beautify -> Skin whitening
Tools -> Beautify -> Rip Border
Tools -> Beautify -> Texture Border

Support: #beautify on FreeNode

